</p>

        </div>

      </header>
      <div class="node__content clearfix">

        
        
            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-news-story-lead field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p><span>The General Assembly designated 22 April as&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.un.org/en/observances/earth-day"><span lang="EN-US">International Mother Earth Day</span></a><span> through a resolution adopted in 2009, but the roots of the Day go back to the 1970s.</span></p>
